<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0081001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0081001">Nisabha 人中牡牛之意。</note>
<note n="0082002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0082002">就同一之比喻見 Cf. S. III, P. 93; A. II, 95; J. I, P. 482。</note>
<note n="0083003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0083003">原語 Singī-nikkha-Suvaṇṇa 皆為黃金。</note>
<note n="0083004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0083004">khadira 樹名。一種硬木。</note>
<note n="0083005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0083005">jotirasa 一種寶石，又為星宿之一（喜宿）。</note>
<note n="0083006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0083006">依暹羅本讀為 Visuddhakelāsasannibho。</note>
<note n="0086001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0086001">jaṅghā 之原意為脚。而塔之脚則應為其基部。</note>
<note n="0086002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0086002">籠蓋（Kañcuka）為塔之全部由磚石等所累積圍攏而成，今再予以增大，此與英語 encasing 相當。</note>
<note n="0086003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0086003">indanīla, mahānīla，皆是青玉之類。</note>
<note n="0087004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0087004">暹羅本於此前加入四偈，說金翅鳥增大塔婆之事，其他情況則相同。</note>
<note n="0087005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0087005">此為有籠蓋之塔，其上再加籠蓋，如此增大塔婆，非為塔上再造塔之意。</note>
<note n="0087006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0087006">密迹，夜叉之一種，手持金剛故，稱密迹金剛等。此處可視為夜叉。</note>
<note n="0087007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0087007">讀為 candasuriyatārakā（異本）。</note>
<note n="0087008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0087008">讀為 Padīpo pana Pajjali（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0088009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0088009">Abhisammata（勝靜）。</note>
<note n="0088010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0088010">訂正為 visuddhā。</note>
<note n="0088011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0088011">讀為 vādaka。</note>
<note n="0088012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0088012">tappara（tatpara）「從彼」者、「……特別專念」者之義。此果意味為佛與否不得而知，而由前後之關係作如是解。原文 P. 534（The rīgāthā, A. l P. 148）中指 Ānanda 有 Buddhupaṭṭhānatappara「奉侍佛之專念者」之義。</note>
<note n="0089013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0089013">讀為 sararvgo va。</note>
<note n="0092001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0092001">讀為 sāmaṁ（異本）。</note>
<note n="0093002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0093002">應讀為 Vandāmi。</note>
<note n="0095001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0095001">註為 adhimattaṁ（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0097001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0097001">過去二十四佛之第十九佛。過去七佛之第一佛。</note>
<note n="0097002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0097002">大砂（Mahāpnḷina）。</note>
<note n="0098001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0098001">Candabhāgā（Candrabhāgā）（月分）。</note>
<note n="0099001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0099001">Bandhumatī（親惠城）。</note>
<note n="0100002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0100002">Sinahavasandana 信度產駿馬所拖拉之馬車。</note>
<note n="0100001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0100001">以下多為略稱 Saraṇa, Sīlagāhaka, Añjalī, Khamadayī。</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
